{"id": 480, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得男子气概是什么？", "description": "徒手打老虎不流行了，试论当代武松何去何从。", "record_count": 7178, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607031300558kQF2ZY315yPOsBG.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-08-13T11:35:30Z", "options": [{"id": 7936, "content": "一个眼神足够", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159601}, {"id": 8448, "content": "男人年轻时一定要撕逼的奋斗，不要到老来跟别的老头在公园下棋，无牛可吹！", "image": "img/option/option/201607021827437OWs2krau91xI0b8.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163972}, {"id": 7937, "content": "haha", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157758}, {"id": 8449, "content": "年轻一定要撕逼奋斗，哪怕结果失败，不要老来无忆可回，无牛可吹！", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182721C2cyEQtbulx8ALHN.jpg", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163972}, {"id": 337665, "content": "坚毅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1301656}, {"id": 7938, "content": "小贝那样，运动，低调，情商高，尊重人，帅气，睿智，温暖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 4119}, {"id": 7939, "content": "温柔地照顾爱人的时候。Being heart-meltingly caring is being fatally attractive to me.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159623}, {"id": 8195, "content": "当你可以的时候，你就这样做了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161238}, {"id": 7940, "content": "温柔。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159623}, {"id": 8196, "content": "做的比说的多 想的比做的多 见的比想的多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161249}, {"id": 9732, "content": "有责任心，有担当，脚踏实地，有自己的想法但也尊重别人的想法。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171521}, {"id": 11524, "content": "做男人该做的必须做的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 178901}, {"id": 7941, "content": "做事果断有魄力", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122404}, {"id": 7943, "content": "全是 Stereotype。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143687}, {"id": 9480, "content": "爷们……淡定……出了事不怕……有爷担着呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170605}, {"id": 7945, "content": "有爱，有责任心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55812}, {"id": 18441, "content": "喜欢一个女人，而不是男人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259101}, {"id": 7946, "content": "正直不偏见，善良有担当。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157608}, {"id": 9230, "content": "包容之心，知性如一", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169126}, {"id": 7954, "content": "有主见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120098}, {"id": 8211, "content": "生死之外皆小事，少说多做，关键时候不怂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148362}, {"id": 8212, "content": "不怕失败，输的起。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161553}, {"id": 8214, "content": "有担当，有责任心，有胆识，型男。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161580}, {"id": 7962, "content": "心有猛虎，细嗅蔷薇", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 60140}, {"id": 7964, "content": "一群屌丝女，各种幻想", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159790}, {"id": 8734, "content": "自己，我，他们。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166369}, {"id": 9250, "content": "简单豁达，有担当。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169658}, {"id": 8483, "content": "万物平等", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164305}, {"id": 14631, "content": "关键时刻有担当 不是话痨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209198}, {"id": 8490, "content": "为天地立心，为生民立命，为往圣继绝学，为万世开太平。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164346}, {"id": 14635, "content": "有担当", "image": "img/option/option/201606052111076M8xVEAbIqmif2Lv.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213632}, {"id": 7983, "content": "有胆实。有担当。有责任心。大方。坚强。勇敢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159875}, {"id": 17199, "content": "杖莫如信", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252160}, {"id": 13876, "content": "有责任有担当", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212970}, {"id": 8501, "content": "粗壮", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163734}, {"id": 8758, "content": "骨子血性，外在卖萌。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155918}, {"id": 8247, "content": "心有猛虎，跪搓衣板", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 71739}, {"id": 9786, "content": "有担当，有责任感吧。千万不能是路痴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171702}, {"id": 13370, "content": "淡定犀利", "image": "img/option/option/20160604235042arYM8G1utlvfENOJ.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164080}, {"id": 56637, "content": "担当、气度、硬", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 351582}, {"id": 7743, "content": "“过去的事，就不要再提了\"", "image": null, "praise_count": 225, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 7999, "content": "尊重女性，孝顺父母，大方干净，谈吐优雅，尊重LGBT，三观正", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115714}, {"id": 8767, "content": "少说多干", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 81059}, {"id": 8513, "content": "好，买！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146366}, {"id": 14657, "content": "我觉得我的同事圈子有一个通病，所有的男同事都比我娘，都没实力可讲", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 207224}, {"id": 8515, "content": "有钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123376}, {"id": 8009, "content": "蜡笔小新", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160012}, {"id": 8014, "content": "有一颗善良的心", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158641}, {"id": 8276, "content": "多看书，多看报，少吃零食多睡觉！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162156}, {"id": 8024, "content": "有担当，敢担当，不管男女都能拥有男子气概", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158812}]}